sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (OCTT)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: TC_043_4_CSMS: Send Local Authorization List - Full
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System supports Local Auth List Management
    Note over CP,CS: Prerequisite: Central System has at least 1 IdToken

    CS->>CP: SendLocalList.req (updateType = Full, localAuthorizationList with idTagInfo)
    Note over CS: Validation: UpdateType should be Full
    Note over CS: Validation: All localAuthorizationList entries have an idTagInfo

    CP-->>CS: SendLocalList.conf (status = Accepted)
    Note over CP: Validation: status is Accepted

    Note over CP,CS: Central System successfully sent a full local authorization list
